      <title>SNB说，现金不再是瑞士的最高付款方式。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/cash-no-longer-is-switzerland-s-top-payment-method-snb-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[借记卡刚好超越了账单和硬币作为瑞士最广泛使用的付款方式，这是一种经济变化，这是一种长期以来因对现金的痴迷而引人注目的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/cash-no-longer-is-switzerland-s-top-payment-method-snb-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 08:11:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
